<author>rynạ wdyʿ, rynạ wdyʿ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fḍlt ạmtlk yswʿ ʿn kl sẖy̱ʾ fy ạldnyạ
 lạ dhb lạ fḍh wlạ mạl klhạ dy ạ̉mwr fạnyh
 wkl knwz ạldnyạ ạlṣdạ wạlsws yfsdhạ
 dạ kfạyh ʿly yswʿ rmyt ạltbr ʿly̱ trạbhạ
 2- fḍlt ạmtlk yswʿ ʿn kl ạlly bygẖryny
 srạbhạ lạ ymkn ykẖdʿny yjdẖbny ạ̉w ygẖwyny
 kl ạlậbạr mtsẖqqh mạ btqdr tḍbṭ myh
 dạ kfạyh ʿly yswʿ ynbwʿ ạlmạyh ạlḥyh
 3- fḍlt ạmtlk yswʿ bạlnʿmh bykfyny
 klạmh dạ bysẖbʿ qlby mwạʿydh btʿzyny
 mn kl qlby ạkẖtrth ykwn wḥdh nṣyby
 dạ kfạyh ʿly yswʿ ạ̹lhy wḥbyby</lyrics>
<title>fḍlt ạmtlk yswʿ</title>
</song>